Younger Sibling (Shalelu)	NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.CampaignTrait.Shalelu	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Younger Sibling (Shalelu)],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CampaignTrait]	DESC:You've lived your whole life in the shadow of your older sister Shalelu, who seems to have the adventure-filled lifestyle you've always wanted for yourself. While your sister always took care of you, she never supported your desire to become an adventurer - Shalelu never explained why, only saying, "Adventuring can cause a lot of pain just as easily as it can bring success and riches." As a younger sibling to one of Sandpoint's more influential citizens, you share some of her innate talent and skill at adventuring. Your quick reflexes give you a +1 trait bonus on all Reflex saving throws. In addition, you gain a +1 trait bonus on all attack rolls against foes that threaten your older sister.																																																																																																																	BONUS:SAVE|Reflex|1|TYPE=Trait										SOURCEPAGE:p.13

